translated: Österberg, Svante Justinus, district clerk, Mariestad, b. 30/1/91 in Kristianstad to Theofil Ö. and Ida Lundström. M. m. Maja Svensson. Children: Karin b. 30, Lars and Sven b. 33. — Bachelor's degree in Lund 16, law studies. Employed by the county council in Mariestad from 20 as a county official, district clerk in the district court of Mariestads fögd in 46. Chairman of the tax committee from 18, secretary of the Vadsbo home history and antiquities association, member of Vadsbo museum. Writings: Marieholm and its county governors (33), Skaraborg fire insurance company 1842-1942, Mariestad savings bank 1821-1946, various essays and articles. Hobby: family research. Member of the Skaraborg fire insurance company since 42.
